first download both code and the video in the same directory.
this code is similar to the scene from the harry potter and the chamber of secrets where harry asks tom riddle's diary
about the chamber of secrets and the diary takes him 50 years back. After running this code and typing in the same sentences
that harry wrote in the diary a new window will appear named python vlc(if you have already have installed that library) and 
that scene will appear on your screen.
